### ============================================
### API de Pacientes - Testes Completos
### ============================================
### Pré-requisito: ter um token JWT válido de um usuário com role DOCTOR
### Total de Endpoints: 14 (8 CRUD + 2 Procedimentos + 4 Buscas)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = seu_jwt_token_aqui

### ============================================
### 1. POST - Criar novo paciente
### ============================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/patients
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "fullName": "João Silva Santos",
  "cpf": "12345678901",
  "birthDate": "1990-05-15",
  "gender": "MALE",
  "bloodType": "O_POSITIVE",
  "phone": "11987654321",
  "email": "joao@email.com",
  "address": "Rua das Flores, 100",
  "city": "São Paulo",
  "state": "SP",
  "zipCode": "01234567",
  "weight": 75.5,
  "height": 1.78
}

### ============================================
### 2. GET - Listar todos os pacientes ativos (paginado)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients?page=0&size=10&sort=fullName,asc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2.1 - Listar com paginação diferente
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients?page=0&size=5&sort=birthDate,desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 3. GET - Buscar paciente por ID
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 4. PUT - Atualizar paciente
### ============================================
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "fullName": "João Silva Santos Junior",
  "cpf": "12345678901",
  "birthDate": "1990-05-15",
  "gender": "MALE",
  "bloodType": "O_POSITIVE",
  "phone": "11988888888",
  "email": "joao.junior@email.com",
  "address": "Rua das Flores, 100 - Apto 501",
  "city": "São Paulo",
  "state": "SP",
  "zipCode": "01234567",
  "weight": 76.0,
  "height": 1.78
}

### ============================================
### 5. DELETE - Excluir paciente (hard delete)
### ============================================
### ⚠️ ATENÇÃO: Esta operação é IRREVERSÍVEL!
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 6. PATCH - Inativar paciente (soft delete)
### ============================================
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/1/inactive
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 7. GET - Buscar pacientes por nome (paginado)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/search/name?name=João&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7.1 - Buscar por parte do nome
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/search/name?name=Silva&page=0&size=10&sort=fullName,asc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 8. GET - Buscar pacientes por CPF (paginado)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/search/cpf?cpf=123&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8.1 - Buscar por CPF completo
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/search/cpf?cpf=12345678901&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 9. GET - Buscar pacientes por e-mail (paginado)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/search/email?email=joao&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9.1 - Buscar por e-mail completo
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/search/email?email=joao@email.com&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 10. GET - Buscar pacientes por telefone (paginado)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/search/phone?phone=119&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10.1 - Buscar por telefone completo
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/search/phone?phone=11987654321&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 11. GET - Filtrar pacientes (múltiplos critérios)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/filter?name=João&gender=MALE&city=São Paulo&state=SP&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11.1 - Filtrar apenas por nome
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/filter?name=Silva&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11.2 - Filtrar apenas por gênero
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/filter?gender=FEMALE&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11.3 - Filtrar por cidade e estado
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/filter?city=Rio de Janeiro&state=RJ&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 12. GET - Listar procedimentos realizados de um paciente
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/1/procedures?page=0&size=10&sort=executionDate,desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12.1 - Listar com paginação diferente
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/1/procedures?page=0&size=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 13. GET - Contar procedimentos realizados de um paciente
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/1/procedures/count
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

